<refsection condition='ref.description'>
<title>Description</title>


<para>This element is a citation to a <tag>RefEntry</tag>.  It must include
a <tag>RefEntryTitle</tag> that should exactly match the title of a 
<tag>RefEntry</tag>.
</para>

<refsection><title>Processing expectations</title>
<para>This element implicitly links to the <tag>RefEntry</tag> with the
same <tag>RefEntryTitle</tag> (in the same volume, as defined by
<tag>ManVolNum</tag>).
</para>
<para><?tdg gentext='format.inline'?>
Usually the <tag>ManVolNum</tag> is put in parentheses.
</para>
</refsection>


